workout.name: Bench Press
workout.explination: exercise in which a lifter lies on a bench with the feet on the floor and raises a weight with both arms.

workout2.name: Squat
workout2.explination: A squat is a strength exercise in which the trainee lowers their hips from a standing position and then stands back up

workout3.name: Deadlift
workout3.explination: a lift made from a standing position, without the use of a bench or other equipment.
